---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Setup Docker">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-10 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Setting Up Docker</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400">
        To run these CTF challenges tailored for our lessons, you need Docker installed on your machine.
        Follow the instructions below for your operating system.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      
      <section class="cyber-card p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13.983 11.078h2.119a.186.186 0 00.186-.185V9.006a.186.186 0 00-.186-.186h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.185.185v1.888c0 .102.083.185.185.185m-2.954-5.43h2.119a.186.186 0 00.186-.186V3.574a.186.186 0 00-.186-.185h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.185.185v1.888c0 .102.083.186.185.186m-2.93 0h2.12a.186.186 0 00.185-.186V3.574a.186.186 0 00-.185-.185h-2.12a.185.185 0 00-.185.185v1.888c0 .102.083.186.185.186m-2.964 0h2.119a.186.186 0 00.185-.186V3.574a.186.186 0 00-.185-.185h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.186.185v1.888c0 .102.084.186.186.186m5.893 2.715h2.119a.186.186 0 00.186-.185V6.29a.186.186 0 00-.186-.185h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.185.185v1.888c0 .102.083.185.185.185m-2.93 0h2.12a.186.186 0 00.185-.185V6.29a.186.186 0 00-.185-.185h-2.12a.185.185 0 00-.184.185v1.888c0 .102.083.185.184.185m-2.964 0h2.119a.186.186 0 00.185-.185V6.29a.186.186 0 00-.185-.185h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.186.185v1.888c0 .102.084.185.186.185m-2.929 0h2.12a.186.186 0 00.186-.185V6.29a.186.186 0 00-.186-.185h-2.12a.185.185 0 00-.185.185v1.888c0 .102.083.185.185.185m2.929 2.715h2.119a.186.186 0 00.186-.186V9.006a.186.186 0 00-.186-.186h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.185.186v1.888c0 .102.083.186.185.186m-2.93 0h2.12a.186.186 0 00.185-.186V9.006a.186.186 0 00-.185-.186h-2.12a.185.185 0 00-.184.186v1.888c0 .102.083.186.184.186m-2.964 0h2.119a.186.186 0 00.185-.186V9.006a.186.186 0 00-.185-.186h-2.119a.185.185 0 00-.186.186v1.888c0 .102.084.186.186.186m-2.929 0h2.12a.186.186 0 00.186-.186V9.006a.186.186 0 00-.186-.186h-2.12a.185.185 0 00-.185.186v1.888c0 .102.083.186.185.186m0 5.337h15.932c.594 0 1.076-.482 1.076-1.076V11.96H.664v3.383c0 .594.482 1.076 1.076 1.076" /></svg>
          Ubuntu / Linux (Recommended)
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm text-slate-300">
          <p>The easiest way to install Docker on Ubuntu is using the convenience script:</p>
          <pre class="bg-black/50 p-4 rounded-lg">curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com -o get-docker.sh
sudo sh get-docker.sh</pre>
          <p>Don't forget to add your user to the docker group so you don't need sudo for every command:</p>
          <pre class="bg-black/50 p-4 rounded-lg">sudo usermod -aG docker $USER</pre>
          <p><em>Log out and log back in for this to take effect.</em></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cyber-card p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Windows & Mac</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
          For Windows and Mac users, we recommend <strong>Docker Desktop</strong>.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/" target="_blank" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center">
          Download Docker Desktop
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
